('9cbef96f-561b-4164-9eda-eebf7dcc0b92', 'Q: Siapa yang dapat mengajukan permohonan informasi publik?', '<p><span class=\"C9DxTc \" style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-size: 16px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-family: Montserrat, Arial;\">A: Setiap warga negara dan/atau badan hukum&nbsp;</span><span class=\"C9DxTc \" style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: none; font-family: Montserrat, Arial;\">I</span><span class=\"C9DxTc \" style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-size: 16px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-family: Montserrat, Arial;\">ndonesia sebagaimana diatur dalam Undang-Undang Repu</span><span class=\"C9DxTc \" style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: none; font-family: Montserrat, Arial;\">blik&nbsp;</span><span class=\"C9DxTc \" style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-size: 16px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-family: Montserrat, Arial;\">Indonesia Nomor 14 Tahun 2008 tentang&nbsp;</span><span class=\"C9DxTc \" style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-size: 16px; font-variant-ligatures: none; font-family: Montserrat, Arial;\">K</span><span class=\"C9DxTc \" style=\"color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-size: 16px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-family: Montserrat, Arial;\">eterbukaan Informasi Publik.</span><br></p>', '2024-08-11 22:27:05', '2024-08-11 22:27:05', '2024-08-11 22:27:05'),
('9cbef9a5-ed3e-4520-86d4-b716601ee09a', 'Q: Apa saja Layanan PPID BAZNAS?', '<p dir=\"ltr\" class=\"zfr3Q CDt4Ke \" style=\"font-variant-ligatures: none; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; outline: none; position: relative; text-decoration-line: inherit; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75; padding-top: 0px;\"><span class=\"C9DxTc \" style=\"font-family: Montserrat, Arial;\">A: PPID BAZNAS memiliki 3 (tiga) jenis layanan, yaitu:</span></p><ol class=\"n8H08c BKnRcf \" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 6px 0px 0px; font-size: 16px;\"><li dir=\"ltr\" class=\"zfr3Q TYR86d lsiHE \" style=\"font-variant-ligatures: none; margin: 0px 0px 0px 15pt; outline: none; position: relative; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-size: 12pt; font-style: inherit; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 0; padding-top: 0px;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\" class=\"zfr3Q CDt4Ke \" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0pt; outline: none; position: relative; text-decoration: inherit; font-size: 12pt; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1.75; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0pt; text-indent: 0pt;\"><a class=\"XqQF9c\" href=\"https://ppid.baznas.go.id/layanan-informasi/formulir/permohonan-informasi\" style=\"color: inherit; text-decoration: none; pointer-events: all;\"><span class=\"C9DxTc \" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255); font-family: Montserrat, Arial; text-decoration-line: underline;\">Layanan Informasi Publik</span></a><span class=\"C9DxTc \" style=\"font-family: Montserrat, Arial;\">&nbsp;: merupakan layanan untuk seluruh masyarakat yang ingin mengajukan permohonan informasi ke BAZNAS;</span></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" class=\"zfr3Q TYR86d lsiHE \" style=\"font-variant-ligatures: none; margin: 6px 0px 0px 15pt; outline: none; position: relative; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); font-size: 12pt; font-